videos.headline: Satterwhite all smiles after this 3-pointer for the Wildcats
videos.description: Northwestern guard Lauryn Satterwhite knocks down a 3-pointer from the wing and cannot contain her excitement heading back the other way.

videos.headline: Evans brings Louisville closer with floater
